        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2920284856" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13549615162420279577">The author’s way with words was truly beautiful. I didn’t care for every poem, but I didn’t expect to. Sometimes you just need to find the right one and there were various right ones. <br/><br/>In some of my favorites, though, the english translation left something to be desired. It just didn’t always translate well. Whether it was the translator or the language difference, I cannot quite tell you. Perhaps it was just that I personally would have said it a different way. But that is the thing with languag</span>
  <span id="freeText13549615162420279577" style="display:none">The author’s way with words was truly beautiful. I didn’t care for every poem, but I didn’t expect to. Sometimes you just need to find the right one and there were various right ones. <br /><br />In some of my favorites, though, the english translation left something to be desired. It just didn’t always translate well. Whether it was the translator or the language difference, I cannot quite tell you. Perhaps it was just that I personally would have said it a different way. But that is the thing with language that you know. It includes your background, your culture, sayings, geography, habits, and meanings beyond simple words. Sometimes you just can’t translate all of that, simply changing a sentence from Spanish to English.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13549615162420279577" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
